      • removeStudent

        public void removeStudent​(Student student)
        A method to remove an existing Student from the database of this application.

        This method will also remove all students from its registered sessions by iterating through its registered Course and all Session under the courses, results of the student will be erased as well.

        Parameters:
        student - Student the student object to be removed.
        See Also:
        Course.getAssessment(), Course.getAllSession(), Session.getStudentRegistered(), Assessment.removeAssessmentResult(Student)

      • removeCourse

        public boolean removeCourse​(Course course)
        A method to remove an existing Course from the database of this application.

        All students that are currently registered to this course will be deregistered.

        Parameters:
        course - Course the course to be removed.
        Returns:
        boolean true if there exist Course to be removed, else false
        See Also:
        Student.deregisterCourse(Course)
